if(wantsPrice){if(/e commerce|ecommerce/.test(context))return isRomanHinglish(q)?'E-commerce website ki price product count, payment gateway, customer accounts, inventory, shipping rules, admin dashboard, integrations, design aur testing par depend karti hai. Exact quotation ke liye ye requirements WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 ya email mohsin.say80@proton.me par share karein.':'E-commerce website pricing depends on product count, payment gateway, customer accounts, inventory, shipping rules, admin dashboard, integrations, design and testing. Share these requirements for an exact quotation on WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 or email mohsin.say80@proton.me.';if(/website|web app|web application/.test(context))return isRomanHinglish(q)?'Website ki price page count, content, custom design, backend, forms, integrations, SEO aur deployment par depend karti hai. Exact quotation ke liye project brief WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 ya email mohsin.say80@proton.me par share karein.':'Website pricing depends on page count, content, custom design, backend, forms, integrations, SEO and deployment. Share a project brief for an exact quotation on WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 or email mohsin.say80@proton.me.';return isRomanHinglish(q)?'Price scope, features, integrations, complexity, testing aur delivery requirements par depend karti hai. Estimate ke liye project brief WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 ya email mohsin.say80@proton.me par share karein.':'Pricing depends on scope, features, integrations, complexity, testing and delivery requirements. Share a project brief on WhatsApp +91 89760 99500 or email mohsin.say80@proton.me for an estimate.'}
